# Cloudflare Pages redirects for the tmw-admin (admin.oftmw.com) deploy ONLY.
# This directory (journal/studio/) is deployed to the tmw-admin project at the
# ROOT, so the studio pages live at /lists, /media, /brain, etc. But the shared
# studio nav links use /studio/* paths (which are correct on www.oftmw.com, where
# the studio is served under /studio/). Strip the prefix here so every /studio/*
# nav link resolves on the admin domain too — including new pages like /brain.
#
# (On the www deploy the project root is journal/, so Pages reads journal/_redirects
#  instead and this file is just an inert static asset — no effect there.)
/studio/*  /:splat  301
